extDesc.message: bitwarden je siguran i besplatan upravitelj lozinki za sve vaše uređaje.

loginOrCreateNewAccount.message: Prijavite se ili stvorite novi račun kako biste pristupili svom sigurnom trezoru.
loginOrCreateNewAccount.description: Log in or create a new account to access your secure vault.

masterPassDesc.message: Glavna lozinka je lozinka koju koristite za pristup vašem trezoru. Vrlo je važno da ne zaboravite glavnu lozinku. Ne postoji način za oporavak lozinke u slučaju da je zaboravite.
masterPassDesc.description: The master password is the password you use to access your vault. It is very important that you do not forget your master password. There is no way to recover the password in the event that you forget it.

masterPassHintDesc.message: Podsjetnik glavne lozinke Vam može pomoći da se prisjetite svoje lozinke ako je zaboravite.
masterPassHintDesc.description: A master password hint can help you remember your password if you forget it.

autoFillInfo.message: Nema dostupnih prijava za automatsko popunjavanje za trenutnu karticu preglednika.
autoFillInfo.description: There are no logins available to auto-fill for the current browser tab.

enterEmailToGetHint.message: Unesite adresu e-pošte svog računa da biste zaprimili podsjetnik za glavnu lozinku.
enterEmailToGetHint.description: Enter your account email address to receive your master password hint.

noFolders.description: There are no folders to list.

emailUsDirectly.message: Pošaljite nam izravno e-poštu kako biste dobili pomoć ili ostavite povratnu informaciju.
emailUsDirectly.description: Email us directly to get help or leave feedback.

visitOurWebsiteDirectly.message: Posjetite našu web stranicu kako biste dobili pomoć, vijesti, e-poštu i / ili saznali više o tome kako koristiti bitwarden.
visitOurWebsiteDirectly.description: Visit our website to get help, news, email us, and/or learn more about how to use bitwarden.

gitHubIssue.message: Otvorite problem u našem GitHub repozitoriju.
gitHubIssue.description: Open an issue at our GitHub repository.

passGenInfo.message: Automatski generirajte jake, jedinstvene zaporke za prijavu.
passGenInfo.description: Automatically generate strong, unique passwords for your logins.

bitWebVaultInfo.message: Upravljajte svojim prijavama s bilo kojeg web-preglednika pomoću bitwarden web trezora.
bitWebVaultInfo.description: Manage your logins from any web browser with the bitwarden web vault.

bitIosVaultInfo.message: Upravljajte svojim prijavama s mobilnih uređaja pomoću bitwarden iOS trezora.
bitIosVaultInfo.description: Manage your logins from your mobile devices with the bitwarden iOS vault.

bitAndrVaultInfo.message: Upravljajte svojim prijavama s mobilnih uređaja pomoću bitwarden Android trezora.
bitAndrVaultInfo.description: Manage your logins from your mobile devices with the bitwarden Android vault.

importLoginsInfo.message: Brzo uvezite svoje prijave iz drugih aplikacija za upravljanje lozinkama.
importLoginsInfo.description: Quickly bulk import your logins from other password management applications.

noLoginsInList.description: There are no logins to list.

rateExtensionDesc.message: Molimo razmislite o tome da nam pomognete s dobrom recenzijom!
rateExtensionDesc.description: Please consider helping us out with a good review!

browserNotSupportClipboard.message: Vaš web preglednik ne podržava jednostavno kopiranje međuspremnika. Umjesto toga ručno kopirajte.
browserNotSupportClipboard.description: Your web browser does not support easy clipboard copying. Copy it manually instead.

masterPassLength.message: Glavna lozinka mora imati najmanje 8 znakova.
masterPassLength.description: Master password must be at least 8 characters long.

masterPassDoesntMatch.description: Master password confirmation does not match.

newAccountCreated.message: Vaš novi račun je kreiran! Sada se možete prijaviti.
newAccountCreated.description: Your new account has been created! You may now log in.

masterPassSent.message: Poslali smo vam e-poštu s podsjetnikom glavne lozinke.
masterPassSent.description: We've sent you an email with your master password hint.

valueCopied.description: ' copied'. This is part of a sentence so be sure to leave the space prefix. For example: 'Password copied'

autofillError.message: Nije moguće automatski ispuniti odabranu prijavu na ovoj stranici. Umjesto toga kopirajte / zalijepite korisničko ime i / ili zaporku.
autofillError.description: Unable to auto-fill the selected login on this page. Copy/paste your username and/or password instead.

logOutConfirmation.message: Jeste li sigurni da se želite odjaviti?
logOutConfirmation.description: Are you sure you want to log out?

changeMasterPasswordConfirmation.message: Možete promijeniti svoju glavnu lozinku na internetskom trezoru bitwarden.com. Želite li sada posjetiti web stranicu?
changeMasterPasswordConfirmation.description: You can change your master password on the bitwarden.com web vault. Do you want to visit the website now?

changeEmailConfirmation.message: Adresu e-pošte možete promijeniti na trezoru web sučelja bitwarden.com. Želite li sada posjetiti web stranicu?
changeEmailConfirmation.description: You can change your email address on the bitwarden.com web vault. Do you want to visit the website now?

twoStepLoginConfirmation.message: Two-step login makes your account more secure by requiring you to verify your login with another device such as a security key, authenticator app, SMS, phone call, or email. Two-step login can be enabled on the bitwarden.com web vault. Do you want to visit the website now?
twoStepLoginConfirmation.description: Two-step login makes your account more secure by requiring you to verify your login with another device such as a security key, authenticator app, SMS, phone call, or email. gettingStartedTutorialVideo.description: Watch our getting started tutorial to learn how to get the most out of the browser extension.

importLoginsConfirmation.message: Možete masovno uvesti prijave sa web-trezora bitwarden.com. Želite li sada posjetiti web stranicu?
importLoginsConfirmation.description: You can bulk import logins from the bitwarden.com web vault. Do you want to visit the website now?

deleteLoginConfirmation.message: Jeste li sigurni da želite izbrisati ovu prijavu?
deleteLoginConfirmation.description: Are you sure you want to delete this login?

overwritePasswordConfirmation.message: Jeste li sigurni da želite prebrisati trenutnu zaporku?
overwritePasswordConfirmation.description: Are you sure you want to overwrite the current password?

credits.description: Credits (giving thanks to people that helped, like at the end of a movie)

noneFolder.description: No Folder - this is the folder for uncategorized logins

gaDesc.message: Koristimo Google Analytics kako bismo saznali na koji način se proširenje upotrebljava kako bismo ga mogli poboljšati. Svako prikupljanje podataka potpuno je anonimno.
gaDesc.description: We use analytics to better learn how the extension is being used so that we can make it better. All data collection is completely anonymous.

addLoginNotificationDesc.message: "Obavijest o dodavanju prijave" automatski vas traži da spremite nove prijave u svoj trezor kad god se prvi put prijavite na njih.
addLoginNotificationDesc.description: The "Add Login Notification" automatically prompts you to save new logins to your vault whenever you log into them for the first time.

disableContextMenuItemDesc.message: Opcije kontekstnog izbotnika omogućuju brzi pristup generiranju lozinke i prijavama za web stranicu na vašoj trenutačnoj kartici.
disableContextMenuItemDesc.description: Context menu options provide quick access to password generation and logins for the website in your current tab.

warning.description: WARNING (should stay in capitalized letters if the language permits)

exportWarning.message: Ovaj izvoz sadrži vaše nešifirane podatke u .csv formatu. Ne biste ga trebali spremati ili poslati preko nesigurnih kanala (kao što je e-pošta). Obrišite ga odmah nakon što ste završili s upotrebom.
exportWarning.description: This export contains your unencrypted data in .csv format. You should not store or send it over unsecure channels (such as email). Delete it immediately after your are done using it.

exportMasterPassword.message: Unesite glavnu lozinku za izvoz podataka iz trezora.
exportMasterPassword.description: Enter your master password to export your vault data.

exportVaultInfo.description: Export your vault data in .csv format so that you can easily modify it or move it elsewhere.

shareVaultInfo.message: Izradite organizaciju kako biste sigurno dijelili svoje prijave s drugim korisnicima.
shareVaultInfo.description: Create an organization to securely share your logins with other users.
